grade_preconditions.et:
1) Aktiivne osavõtt tundidest (vähemalt 75% kontakttunde);
2) Nelja testi edukas sooritamine (vähemalt 60% õigeid vastuseid iga testi kohta; 
3) Igat  testi on võimalik järele teha semestri lõpus ühe korra;
4) Kodutöö on õigeaegselt esitatud (Antes y ahora); 
3) Loetud üks raamat.

PASSED: The student has read the text proposed by the teacher, has looked up the pronunciation and the meaning of new words, is able to answer to the questions about its content and is able to translate a passage chosen by the teacher into English or Estonian.
FAILED: The student has not presented the home reading or has done it insufficiently.
